The most-restrictive upstream sources used here — Ookla Speedtest Open Data
and the GEM Seismic Hazard Map (open release) — are CC BY-NC-SA 4.0. License
compatibility requires that any combined output be licensed at least as
restrictively. CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 is the lowest common denominator that respects
every upstream license.

